624
00:45:48,260 --> 00:45:50,180
This is not what I want to hear!

625
00:45:50,180 --> 00:45:52,600
All I want is a proper explanation!

626
00:45:52,600 --> 00:45:53,880
As a prince,

627
00:45:53,880 --> 00:45:58,360
you only know how to create strife.

628
00:45:58,360 --> 00:46:01,125
Don't think that I don't know what you are trying to do.

629
00:46:01,125 --> 00:46:05,040
Teaching 10th Brother to lead the Zhangs into defying an Imperial order!

630
00:46:05,040 --> 00:46:07,760
Don't treat my compassion as a weakness!

631
00:46:15,380 --> 00:46:17,082
They are all blood-related brothers

632
00:46:17,082 --> 00:46:20,999
